data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER - MOVE IN READY HOME - MOTIVATED SELLER - .... Lifestyle Move? This is the home to come see.. BEAUTIFUL BRICK, CORNER LOT, Spacious OPEN concept Floor Plan.   3 CAR GARAGE, 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, High ceilings, recessed lighting...  Many KITCHEN cabinets w/Granite countertops & under cabinet lighting. Looking for a LARGE backyard? Its here too! COVERED PATIO , Great for entertaining. Come & build your private swimming pool! Oh, did I mention the low tax rate?? Convenient to I-69, 242, Grand Parkway,  Find Dining & Shopping easy @Valley Ranch Town Center. SCHEDULE A SHOWING TODAY.
